race.description: Tle Electrical Jungle Juice Cup Conditional Hcp
race.comment: SONOFDEC (1) has returned in much better order this prep. Scored a tough win in heavy going first-up at Kembla then missed the kick before charging home to just miss over 1300m at this track last start. Holds the form at the third run of the prep as a rule so he looks the one to beat. EARL OF BANTRY (4) has also been highly impressive this time in work, making it two wins from three last time when he led from the outset in a game performance over 1280m at Muswellbrook. Tricky gate but otherwise difficult to fault. WHETU (3) last appeared when down the track over 2000m at Wyong nine weeks ago. Will be better for this run but might surprise while fresh. RAJNISH (6) was too bad to be true in the Dubbo Cup recently. Lead up form was good so give him another chance. The promising DASHING RUPERT (2) has won two from two when fresh so keep him safe first-up from a five-month break.
